article_title: Tim Tebow's highlights from Week 1 of preseason 2015
article_text:
Philadelphia Eagles quarterback Tim Tebow debut with the Philadelphia Eagles elicited huge cheers from the hometown crowd. Not bad for a fourth-string quarterback fighting for a roster spot.

Tebow, a first-round draft pick by the Denver Broncos, completed 6-of-12 passes for 69 yards, and ran in for a touchdown as the Eagles won 36-10 over Indianapolis on Sunday.
